name: sa4_w16f_occ_by_tot_prs_inc_by_age_census_2016
title: SA4-W16f Occupation by Total Personal Income (weekly) by Age-Census 2016

legal.licenceType: Creative Commons Attribution 2.5 Australia (CC BY 2.5 AU)

abstract:
SA4 based data for Occupation by Total Personal Income (Weekly) by Age, in Working Population Profile (WPP), 2016 Census. Count of employed persons aged 15 years and over. W16 is broken up into 8 sections (W16a - W16h), this section contains 'Machinery operators and drivers Total Age 20-24 years' - 'Occupation inadequately described Not stated $500-$649 Age 25-34 years'. The data is by SA4 2016 boundaries. Periodicity: 5-Yearly.
Note: There are small random adjustments made to all cell values to protect the confidentiality of data. These adjustments may cause the sum of rows or columns to differ by small amounts from table totals.
For more information visit the data source: http://www.abs.gov.au/census.
